# COSIGN
# Private key must never be committed. In a CI/CD pipeline, store the key
# content as a GitHub Secret (COSIGN_PRIVATE_KEY) and the password as
# COSIGN_PASSWORD — same pattern as GCP_SA_KEY in Lab 1.
